gate: OPEN
sprint: S05
track: B
task: B6
title: "feat(checkout): runtime CNH-overnight cost parity check vs BE /rates (#1437)"
repos: [crop-front]
priority: medium
refs:
  - CROP-front#1437
  - CROP-front#978  (parent umbrella)
  - S05-A5          (shared constants must be available)
requires: [NEXTJS_VERCEL_FRONTEND]

description: |
  FE displays CNH-overnight price from shared constants. If BE /rates returns a
  different value (drift or surcharge), customer sees wrong price. After fetching
  /rates, compare BE overnight rate against FE constant. On mismatch: show BE
  value (source of truth) + fire Sentry warning with delta.

scope:
  in:
    - Checkout overnight rate fetch — add post-fetch comparison
    - Mismatch: display BE rate + Sentry.captureMessage with delta
    - Unit test: matching → no warning; mismatched → Sentry + BE rate shown
  out:
    - BE /rates logic changes
    - Alerts outside Sentry

invariants:
  - BE /rates is always source of truth on mismatch
  - Sentry event must not include raw pricing beyond delta amount

acceptance:
  - Rate match: no Sentry event, FE shows constant value
  - Rate mismatch: FE shows BE value, Sentry warning with delta
  - Unit tests cover both paths

dep: B5 + A5 + A3
output: checkout overnight rate fetch patched + unit tests
